	<h1 class="title">没人能够证明冷压果汁对你更好，但它还是流行了起来</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/998/small/998.jpg?1402274915" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐云路</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-04-09 08:06:47 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/8254/medium/8254.jpg?1436696080" alt="" />			
	</div>
